OL,3,CExplosions heard as dozens of
OL,4,Cemergency responders tackle building
OL,5,Cfire
OL,7,FFootage from Dan Jessup shows the fire
OL,8,Fblazing overnight in East Hoathly.
OL,10,FThree barns in rural Sussex have been
OL,11,Fdestroyed in a major fire which spread
OL,12,Facross a farm overnight in East
OL,13,FHoathly.
OL,15,FResidents reported being woken by the
OL,16,Fsound of explosions from cylinders
OL,17,Fwhich caught light in the buildings.
OL,18,FEmergency services received more than
OL,19,Fsixty calls from locals about the
OL,20,Fincident
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/3
