OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1778144787
OL,3,CExplosions heard as dozens of
OL,4,Cemergency responders tackle building
OL,5,Cfire
OL,7,FAt its height, six appliances from
OL,8,FEast Sussex Fire and Rescue Service
OL,9,Fwere dispatched to tackle the flames
OL,10,Flate on Tuesday evening (May 5). A
OL,11,F200m exclusion zone was established to
OL,12,Favoid any injuries from the explosions.
OL,14,FAn Incident Command Unit was also set-
OL,15,Fup near the site just after midnight.
OL,17,FNo injuries have been reported and
OL,18,Feveryone has been accounted for.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/3
