OL,3,CExplosions heard as dozens of
OL,4,Cemergency responders tackle building
OL,5,Cfire
OL,7,FWith the fire under now control, a
OL,8,Fsingle crew has been tasked with
OL,9,Fmonitoring the site as the buildings
OL,10,Fare left to extinguish as part of a
OL,11,Fcontrolled burn.
OL,13,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,14,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,15,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,16,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,17,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,18,Fbelow...
